300.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Can be unlocked by collecting points from Returnee Missions. </color>
(Lasts for 30 days)
300.name: Leader

301.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Welcome back to the Admiralty, Commander. We expect great things from you.</color>
(Lasts for 30 days)
301.name: Returnee

302.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Red blood and cold iron temper our indomitable will."</color>
Obtained from the "Scherzo of Iron and Blood" event.
302.name: The Iron Blood Oath

303.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"For our azure freedom! God bless the Eagle Union!"</color>
Obtained from the "Ashen Simulacrum" event.
303.name: Wings of Freedom

304.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Display the glory and dignity of the Sardegna Empire to the whole world!"</color>
Obtained from the "Empyreal Tragicomedy" event.
304.name: Insignia of Glory

305.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"With this offering, we pray for a bright future for the Sakura Empire."</color>
Obtained from the "Swirling Cherry Blossoms" event.
305.name: Sakura Ceremony

306.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Unite, comrades! The world is ours to change!"</color>
Obtained from the "Northern Overture" event.
306.name: Proof of Solidarity

307.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"O, fearless thunderbolts of liberty! Guide us through the darkness!"</color>
Obtained from the "Microlayer Medley" event.
307.name: Wings of Lightning

308.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"May numerous hymns cross the seas to reach the skies... Vive la Iris!"</color>
Obtained from the "Skybound Oratorio" event.
308.name: Iris Canto

309.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"For the glory of Her Majesty and the Royal Navy!"</color>
Obtained from the "Aurora Noctis" event.
309.name: Royal Crown

310.desc:
<color=#ffffff>A special portrait frame designed with Laffey's motifs.</color>
Obtained from the 2nd Anniversary event.
310.name: Laffey's Gift

311.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"May the light of hope shine forevermore, whether in reality or in a dream."</color>
Obtained from "Dreamwaker's Butterfly" event.
311.name: Illusory Butterfly

312.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"May my red blood flow into the frigid mold of war."</color>
Obtained from the "Inverted Orthant" event.
312.name: Weapon of the Iron Blood

313.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"The Sirens' secrets shall dance in the palm of our hand!"</color>
Obtained from the "Khorovod of Dawn's Rime" event.
313.name: Seal of Dawn's Rime

314.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Come, and become a pillar for our reborn empire! Let us seize glory together! "</color>
Obtained from the "Daedalian Hymn" event.
314.name: Pride of Sardegna

315.desc:
<color=#ffffff>The indomitable Black Dragon of the Eagle Union has arrived! Together, let us shake the foundations of this world!</color>
Obtained from the "Mirror involution" event.
315.name: Voltaic Lightwings

316.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Well, this is SOME kind of treasure, I suppose."</color>
Obtained from the "Upon the Shimmering Blue" event.
316.name: Ryugu's Acknowledgment

317.desc: <color=#ffffff>A bridge that spans beyond reality. Is it Heaven or Hell that awaits us on the other side?</color>Obtained from the "Tower of Transcendence" event.
317.name: Mark of Transcendence

318.desc:
<color=#ffffff>An award given by Sovetsky Soyuz to soldiers who went above and beyond.</color>
 Obtained from the "Abyssal Refrain" event.
318.name: Seal of the Polar Star

319.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Beyond the open door lies a new future.</color>
Obtained from the "Rondo at Rainbow's End" event
319.name: Singularity at Rainbow's End

320.desc:
<color=#ffffff>War and time may take their tolls, but our pledges will shine on like stars in the night sky.</color>
Obtained from the "Pledge of the Radiant Court" event.
320.name: Seal of the Radiant Court

321.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Though its path may be filled with thorns, the aquila of Sette Colli still spreads its wings and takes flight.</color>
Obtained from the "Aquilifer's Ballade" event.
321.name: Splendor of Sardegna

322.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"From sea of cloud comes lonely rays, as fleeting as the morning haze. From its scabbard does heavenly sword draw, a violet flash sundering sky, earth, and all."</color>
Obtained from the "Violet Tempest, Blooming Lycoris" event.
322.name: Violet Lightning Storm

323.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Space and time intertwine amidst spinning rings, and destiny converges within the pillar of light."</color>
Obtained from the "Parallel Superimposition" event.
323.name: Sea of Stars Loop

324.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"It is not Divinity we seek, but rather the light of Her Majesty's blessings–"</color>
Obtained from the "Revelations of Dust" event.
324.name: Seal of Divine Refulgence

325.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"On the prophesied day, fall into raging flames and billowing waves––"</color>
Awarded to Commanders who participated in the "Confluence of Nothingness" event.
325.name: Norn's Synthetic Loop

326.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Even without laurels atop their head, those who uphold true faith shall be crowned with victory."</color>
–"The Fool's Scales" event reward.
326.name: Unbestowed Crown

327.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Life, even if brief, is hard to substitute–"</color>
Obtained from the "Effulgence Before Eclipse" event.
327.name: Wisteria Seal

328.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"The heaven that covers all, the causality that replicates the world. Cross the line in the sand and let the eternal truth be impressed upon all."</color>
Obtained from the "Light-Chasing Sea of Stars" event.
328.name: Light-Chasing Ring of Stars

329.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"Through the snow, across the icebergs, look at yourself and witness the future."</color>
Given to Commanders who excelled during the "Snowrealm Peregrination" event.
329.name: Star of the Snowrealm

330.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"I will continue choosing to protect, even in a transient dream."</color>
Given to Commanders who participated in the "Light of the Martyrium" event.
330.name: Dreambound Martyr

331.desc:
<color=#ffffff>A resplendent heart that never stops. A gale of iron blowing through the waves.</color>
Given to Commanders who participated in the Windborne Steel Wings event.
331.name: Resplendent Heart

332.desc:
<color=#ffffff>"The phoenix dances when the fox roars, bathing in flames and receiving new flesh. Though lives change, memories do not."</color> 
Given to Commanders who participated in the Ode of Everblooming Crimson event.
332.name: Flames of Resurrection

406.name: Hall of Fame: Laffey

501.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Let your love for delicious pizza be known by all!</color>
―Obtained in the "Manjuu Pizzeria" event.
501.name: Manjuu Pizzeria Frame

601.desc:
<color=#ffffff>I scream, you scream, we all scream for ice cream.</color>
Obtained from the "Manjuu Ice Cream" event.
601.name: A Song of Ice and Cream

602.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Set sail for the best deserted island vacation ever!</color>
Awarded to Commanders who participated in the "Uncharted Summer" event.
602.name: Summer and Seabreeze

603.desc:
<color=#ffffff>A commemorative frame that brings back memories of laughter and champagne.</color>
–"Castle of Celebrations" event reward.
603.name: Effervescent Emblem

605.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Victory belongs to who reaches the goal fastest.</color>
Awarded to Commanders who participated in the "High-Speed Raceway" event.
605.name: Seal of the Speedster

606.desc: <color=#ffffff>Feel the breeze, take in the sun, and enjoy yourself!</color> Obtained in the "Pleasure, Leisure, and Treasure" event.
606.name: Ring of Leisure

607.desc: <color=#ffffff>No one can escape their own story. Not even a free-spirited rider.</color> Given to Commanders who participated in the Wild West Vacation Log event.
607.name: A Trip to the Prairie

1001.desc:
<color=#ffffff>In every bite, a sweet and delectable memory.</color>
Obtained by raising Intimacy Level with Sirius in Private Quarters.
1001.name: Sweet Rendezvous

1002.desc:
<color=#ffffff>Whatever happens, there will always be a cup of warm tea quietly waiting for you.</color>
Obtained by raising Intimacy Level with Sirius in Private Quarters.
1002.name: Afternoon Tea
